language Essence 1.3

given w: int(1..)
given g: int(1..)
given s: int(1..)
letting nGolfers be g * s
find sched: matrix indexed by [int(1..w), int(1..nGolfers)] of int(1..g)
such that and([and([sum([toInt(sched[i, p] = j) | p : int(1..nGolfers)]) = s | j : int(1..g)]) | i : int(1..w)])
such that
    and([and([p1 < p2 -> sum([toInt(sched[i, p1] = sched[i, p2]) | i : int(1..w)]) <= 1 | p2 : int(1..nGolfers)])
             | p1 : int(1..nGolfers)])

